**Bucky's Barrel Bash**

- Requirements:
- Include a player-controlled character that can move left and right.
- The player shall be able to jump to avoid obstacles and reach higher platforms.
- Consist of multiple stacked platforms connected by ladders.
- The player shall be able to climb ladders to move between platform levels.
- Include an enemy at the top of the tower that throws obstacles downward.
- Include moving obstacles (e.g., barrels) that roll across platforms.
- Contact with an obstacle shall result in the player losing a life.
- The player shall start the game with a limited number of lives.
- End the game when the player runs out of lives.
- Track and display the playerâ€™s score.
- The score shall increase when the player avoids obstacles or climbs higher.
- Include a win condition when the player reaches the top platform.
- Increase game difficulty by increasing obstacle speed or frequency.
- Include a start screen and a game-over screen.
